body_html:
The "MNIST For ML Beginners" has most equations working, but there's several in the Training section that are showing "Math Processing Error":

https://www.tensorflow.org/versions/r0.7/tutorials/mnist/beginners/index.html#training

Error: Cannot read property 'fontInherit' of undefined
Debugging tips: use 'unpacked/MathJax.js', inspect 'MathJax.Hub.lastError' in the browser console

Using Mathjax's right-click menu to set the Renderer to SVG works, so it's just the HTML+CSS renderer having issues.
